# === K8s secrets materialised locally from placeholders ===
# The tracked secrets.yaml files contain REPLACE_WITH_* placeholders.
# `make update-secrets` substitutes real values in-place from .env; these
# mutated copies must never be committed back. Uncomment the block below
# if you prefer to keep untouched placeholder files tracked and ignore
# any locally-mutated variants (recommended for multi-developer setups):
# k8s/base/api-gateway/gateway-secrets.yaml
# k8s/base/ml-pipeline/secrets.yaml
# k8s/base/service-selection/db-secrets.yaml
# k8s/base/service-selection/kaggle-secrets.yaml
# k8s/base/service-selection/storage-secrets.yaml
# k8s/base/xai-engine/secrets.yaml
